                                    <li>Aging Report</li>
                                    <li>Type Distribution</li>
                                    <li>Value Analysis</li>
                                    <li>High-Value Requisitions</li>
                                    <li>Requester Activity</li>
                                    <li>Approval Turnaround Time</li>
                                    <li>Pending Actions by User/Role</li>
